comment.author: 47524421@N08
comment._content: Ford 4-AT-E NC9612 c/n 4-AT-55 Mamer Flight Service, Spokane, to RG Pattinson & W Parmenter, St Elmo, then to K-T Flying Service, Honolulu.  This aircraft is currently preserved as 'Evergreen International - City of McMinnville' at Evergreen Aviation Museum, McMinnville, Oregon.
